#### 3.1 html 和 body

```css
html {
    font-size: 16px;
}

html,
body {
    -webkit-text-size-adjust: 100%;
    -ms-text-size-adjust: 100%;
    fill: currentColor;
    line-height: 1.625rem;
    background-image: url(./image/ims.webp);
